item.title: Well, that worked!
item.description: So the site is live! I will admit, I am not particularly savvy when it comes to JavaScript frameworks. I am primarily a C# developer yet here we are. So, let me introduce myself. I’m Jordan, a twenty two year old automated test engineer based in Victoria, Australia.
